          <lastSummaryUpdateDate>2020-02-03T13:42:17Z</lastSummaryUpdateDate>
          <text><![CDATA[<p><b>Blocking Investment In Our Adversaries Act</b></p> <p>This bill limits the investments of the International Stock Index Investment Fund (I Fund) under the Thrift Savings Plan.</p> <p>Specifically, it prohibits the I Fund from investing in any entity based in a peer or near-peer competitor nation, including China or Russia. </p>]]></text>
          <updateDate>2019-05-22T04:00:00Z</updateDate>
          <name>Introduced in House</name>
        </item>
